WEBVTT

00:00.003 --> 00:03.504
And perhaps, the debt crisis might be solved with more Jobs.

00:03.595 --> 00:06.287
As in Steve Jobs, the CEO of Apple.

00:06.653 --> 00:10.121
The latest earnings report from the world's most highly - valued tech company shows...

00:10.435 --> 00:13.731
...cash reserves of more than 76 billion dollars.

00:14.098 --> 00:18.314
The US Treasury has reserves just under 74 billion.

00:18.733 --> 00:21.222
These figures may not be directly comparable,...

00:21.327 --> 00:23.718
...since Apple's number is based on its ready cash,...

00:24.083 --> 00:28.554
...while the US figure is how much it has before hitting the debt ceiling.

